Subject: [PATCH 03/14] Add include directory with symbolic link

An include directory was created with the `ssc` directory that links to the repository root. This was done to make all includes local to the shader compiler so that Skyline's include folder wouldn't be filled with arbitrary headers.
---
 include/shader_compiler | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)
 create mode 120000 include/shader_compiler

diff --git a/include/shader_compiler b/include/shader_compiler
new file mode 120000
index 0000000..a96aa0e
--- /dev/null
+++ b/include/shader_compiler
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+..
\ No newline at end of file
